{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":19482,"duration_api_ms":18557,"ttft_ms":11459,"num_turns":2,"result":"CLI が `should_stop=true`（`dirty_or_stale_source`）を返したため、ここで停止します。\n\n---\n\n## CLI ブロック通知\n\n**ブロック理由:** `dirty_or_stale_source`（ソース仕様が更新済みまたは未処理の変更あり）\n\n**推奨される次のアクション（CLI 原文）:**\n> `run /spec-core before /spec-realign`\n\n### 対応手順\n\n先に `/spec-core` を実行してソースを再処理・再インデックスしてから、もう一度 `/spec-realign` を実行してください。\n\n```\n/spec-core\n```\n\n完了後:\n```\n/spec-realign 認証とセッションに関する回答を整形して。回答案: 認証後はセッション cookie を発行し、ログアウト時に無効化する。\n```","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"ff7cd3fb-bf7a-431b-a6a6-fe44452cc639","total_cost_usd":0.07798365000000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14309,"cache_read_input_tokens":38843,"output_tokens":844,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":14309,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":246,"cache_read_input_tokens":25373,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2406,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2406},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":4,"outputTokens":844,"cacheReadInputTokens":38843,"cacheCreationInputTokens":14309,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.07798365000000002,"contextWindow":400000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"520e100c-7ba9-4a26-b079-c762fcd49c58"}
